@host = http://localhost:3000
@recurso = galeria

### busca fotos e videos
GET {{host}}/{{recurso}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### busca fotos
GET {{host}}/{{recurso}}/fotos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### busca videos
GET {{host}}/{{recurso}}/videos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### salva fotos 
